//In this novelization of our Academy-Award winning film//, Messiah, //compiled by our specialists, we present to you exclusive details about the internal workings of the film,[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]This does not appear in any of the copies.[[/span]] brought to you by the VKTM.//

Janus is a simple farmer working in the country of Raen, in the continent of Ester. However things turn out to be not-so-simple when he realizes he's the next incarnation of Sezuz, and he must unite the world

Or die trying...

